    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the kale is starting to soften, add the <strong>spinach</strong> with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for a further 3-4 min or until the kale is tender and the spinach is starting to wilt – these are your <strong>garlic greens</strong></p>",
