      "instruction": "<p>Peel the <strong>cooled boiled egg[s]</strong> and cut them in half</p><p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the stone[s]</p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong> using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and slice finely</p>",
