    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sweet potato wedges</strong> with the <strong>garlic greens</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>avocado</strong>, <strong>boiled egg halves</strong> and <strong>lemon wedge</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>mustard dressing</strong> and sprinkle with the <strong>tamari-roasted seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
